<InnerPageLayout
  title="The ASE Paradigm — Empower AI"
  description="Agentic Semantic Engineering isn't faster coding — it's a different level of work. Compare skills, abstraction, scalability, determinism, and governance between agentic coding and ASE."
  heroLabel="The ASE Paradigm"
  heroTitle="Agentic Coding Is Still Coding. This Is What Comes Next."
  heroSubtitle="The shift from agentic coding to Agentic Semantic Engineering isn't about speed or savings. It's about operating at a fundamentally different level — where you specify meaning, and the code writes itself."
