  <section class="inner-section container">
    <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>The Economics Follow the Paradigm</h2>
          <p>When you operate at a higher abstraction level, the economic advantages aren't accidental — they're structural. Every dimension of ASE's paradigm advantage maps to a measurable token reduction:</p>
          <div class="economics-links">
            <div class="econ-link">
              <span class="econ-arrow">&rarr;</span>
